Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:32.34,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直诉说着的自我风格
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:36.43,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但也搞不太懂究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:43.68,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}迷失在露出扭曲笑容和叹息的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:45.56,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:50.31,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果在"这个世界"印象的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:54.65,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有着不同的世界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:23:00.24,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要找出所有重要的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.99,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}亲眼地确认
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.99,0:23:06.37,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Please Please Me 请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:10.46,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要伸出双手拥抱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:14.42,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let me free 请露出笑容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:18.59,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}答案一直都在镜像之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:22.30,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}呆呆地仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.30,0:23:25.68,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊啊 月色真美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:30.02,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望这梦永不结束
